SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT * FROM (select 'A' AP,LINE_NO,A_TYPE,A_ACCOUNT_NO,A_COLUMN,A_DESCRIPTION,A_FONT_STYLE,A_NOTES, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_01),0)/:6 SALDO_01, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_02),0)/:6 SALDO_02, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_03),0)/:6 SALDO_03, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_04),0)/:6 SALDO_04, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_05),0)/:6 SALDO_05, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_06),0)/:6 SALDO_06, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_07),0)/:6 SALDO_07, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_08),0)/:6 SALDO_08, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_09),0)/:6 SALDO_09, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_10),0)/:6 SALDO_10, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_11),0)/:6 SALDO_11, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_12),0)/:6 SALDO_12, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_13),0)/:6 SALDO_13 from GL_BSHETRGD R (nolock) left join GL_BALANCE B (nolock) on B.CO_ID=R.CO_ID and B.BR_ID=:1 and FISCAL_YEAR=:2 and CURR_ID=':3' AND ACCOUNT_NO=A_ACCOUNT_NO AND B.COST_CENTER=:7 WHERE R.CO_ID=':4' AND REPORT_NO=:5 AND A_TYPE<>'P' GROUP BY LINE_NO,A_TYPE,A_ACCOUNT_NO,A_COLUMN,A_DESCRIPTION,A_FONT_STYLE,A_NOTES UNION ALL select 'P',LINE_NO,P_TYPE,P_ACCOUNT_NO,P_COLUMN,P_DESCRIPTION,P_FONT_STYLE,P_NOTES, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_01),0)/:6 SALDO_01, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_02),0)/:6 SALDO_02, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_03),0)/:6 SALDO_03, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_04),0)/:6 SALDO_04, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_05),0)/:6 SALDO_05, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_06),0)/:6 SALDO_06, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_07),0)/:6 SALDO_07, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_08),0)/:6 SALDO_08, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_09),0)/:6 SALDO_09, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_10),0)/:6 SALDO_10, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_11),0)/:6 SALDO_11, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_12),0)/:6 SALDO_12, ISNULL(SUM(ENDING_13),0)/:6 SALDO_13 from GL_BSHETRGD R (nolock) left join GL_BALANCE B (nolock) on B.CO_ID=R.CO_ID and B.BR_ID=:1 and FISCAL_YEAR=:2 and CURR_ID=':3' AND ACCOUNT_NO=P_ACCOUNT_NO AND B.COST_CENTER=:7 WHERE R.CO_ID=':4' AND REPORT_NO=:5 AND P_TYPE<>'P' AND A_TYPE<>'' AND P_TYPE<>'' GROUP BY LINE_NO,P_TYPE,P_ACCOUNT_NO,P_COLUMN,P_DESCRIPTION,P_FONT_STYLE,P_NOTES union all select LINE_TYPE,LINE_NO,P_TYPE,P_ACCOUNT_NO,P_COLUMN,P_DESCRIPTION,P_FONT_STYLE,P_NOTES, sum(ENDING_01),sum(ENDING_02),sum(ENDING_03),sum(ENDING_04),sum(ENDING_05),sum(ENDING_06),sum(ENDING_07),sum(ENDING_08),sum(ENDING_09),sum(ENDING_10),sum(ENDING_11),sum(ENDING_12),sum(ENDING_13) FROM ( SELECT LINE_TYPE,R.LINE_NO,X.P_TYPE,X.P_ACCOUNT_NO,X.P_DESCRIPTION,X.P_COLUMN,X.P_FONT_STYLE,X.P_NOTES, ISNULL(ENDING_01,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_01, ISNULL(ENDING_02,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_02, ISNULL(ENDING_03,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_03, ISNULL(ENDING_04,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_04, ISNULL(ENDING_05,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_05, ISNULL(ENDING_06,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_06, ISNULL(ENDING_07,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_07, ISNULL(ENDING_08,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_08, ISNULL(ENDING_09,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_09, ISNULL(ENDING_10,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_10, ISNULL(ENDING_11,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_11, ISNULL(ENDING_12,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_12, ISNULL(ENDING_13,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_13 FROM GL_BSHETRGP R (nolock) LEFT JOIN GL_BSHETRGD D (nolock) ON D.CO_ID=R.CO_ID AND D.REPORT_NO=R.REPORT_NO AND D.LINE_NO=R.FROM_LINE_NO LEFT JOIN GL_BSHETRGD X (nolock) ON X.CO_ID=R.CO_ID AND X.REPORT_NO=R.REPORT_NO AND X.LINE_NO=R.LINE_NO LEFT JOIN GL_BALANCE B (nolock) ON B.CO_ID=D.CO_ID AND B.BR_ID=:1 AND FISCAL_YEAR=:2 AND ACCOUNT_NO=D.P_ACCOUNT_NO AND CURR_ID=':3' WHERE R.CO_ID=':4' AND R.REPORT_NO=:5 AND LINE_TYPE='P' AND X.P_TYPE='P' AND B.COST_CENTER=:7 ) Y group by LINE_TYPE,LINE_NO,P_TYPE,P_ACCOUNT_NO,P_COLUMN,P_DESCRIPTION,P_FONT_STYLE,P_NOTES)C :8 ORDER BY AP,LINE_NO
